{"tid":2337314,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"原來打乞痴係咁","createTime":"2020-12-23T07:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T08:54:43.000Z","uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b76c2a59b738e614e3e5032fe1ac8a271996918a","tid":2337314,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:59:12.000Z","msg":"反射的感受器在鼻黏膜，由三叉神經傳導到腦部。打噴嚏前，鼻子變得發酸、發癢。過程一般為急促吸氣，張嘴，然後高速（可達每小時50公里）通過鼻腔和口腔同時排氣，產生響亮的「阿─嚏」聲音（粵語中以「乞嗤」形聲表示）。打噴嚏時，唾液會形成1000-40000粒飛沫隨空氣高速噴出，速度達每小時177公里（即每秒約49.2米）[1]，所以是很多傳染病的傳染媒介。一般打噴嚏的同時還會閉眼，可能是為了避免飛沫污染。直徑大於100微米的飛沫很快落地，小粒飛沫水分部分蒸發後，形成氣溶膠，可以懸浮幾個小時或更長。"},{"pid":"75f4a495df76aa6e1612faf63d4a84954420bb4c","tid":2337314,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"咁破產係點架"},{"pid":"e05623d5e182c1884ee889ca4e6f78c69565b46e","tid":2337314,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src